/*==============================================================================

    Summary

==============================================================================*/
.caption
Summary
.end

.body
The sample project will serve as a template from which you can create any
application you like. If you are interested, you can learn about the basic
concepts in building ReactJava apps by exploring the
%markup%<a href="ReactJavaWebsite.html#UserGuide">Tutorial</a>%markup%.
.end
